<tr id="L323"><td><a href="#L323">323</a></td><td>KIRK:  Yes, Sheriff. I want you to stop the fight.</td></tr>

<tr id="L324"><td><a href="#L324">324</a></td><td>BEHAN:  Stop it? Who wants to stop it? I sure don't. You don't. You didn't yesterday.</td></tr>

<tr id="L325"><td><a href="#L325">325</a></td><td>KIRK:  I do now.</td></tr>

<tr id="L326"><td><a href="#L326">326</a></td><td>BEHAN:  Since when does a Clanton run crawling to the law for help?</td></tr>

<tr id="L327"><td><a href="#L327">327</a></td><td>KIRK:  How else is he going to get justice?</td></tr>

<tr id="L328"><td><a href="#L328">328</a></td><td>BEHAN:  (indicating gun) From this. You and your boys set up this whole thing to take care of the Earps. It's a little late to decide you don't have the belly for it.</td></tr>

<tr id="L329"><td><a href="#L329">329</a></td><td>KIRK:  It's not too late. Sheriff. Sheriff. There must be plenty of decent people in town who don't like the Earps. Let's organise them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L330"><td><a href="#L330">330</a></td><td>BEHAN:  Don't talk nonsense. The people in this town are counting on you to get rid of the Earps for them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L331"><td><a href="#L331">331</a></td><td>KIRK:  Then the people had better wake up and let the law work for them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L332"><td><a href="#L332">332</a></td><td>BEHAN:  You can talk that way after what the Earps did to Billy today? Nobody in this town will deny you your right to your revenge.</td></tr>

<tr id="L333"><td><a href="#L333">333</a></td><td>KIRK:  Yes, I want revenge. I want to crush the life out of the Earps. But I can't just kill them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L334"><td><a href="#L334">334</a></td><td>BEHAN:  You listen to me. Get down to the OK Corral. Keep out of sight. When the Earps come looking, you bushwhack them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L335"><td><a href="#L335">335</a></td><td>KIRK:  Can't I get it through your stupid head? I can't just kill them! I can't murder them!</td></tr>

<tr id="L336"><td><a href="#L336">336</a></td><td>BEHAN:  It's the only way.</td></tr>

<tr id="L337"><td><a href="#L337">337</a></td><td>KIRK:  I can't kill them! I can't kill them!</td></tr>

<tr id="L338"><td><a href="#L338">338</a></td><td>BEHAN:  Kill them any way you can! There'll be no questions asked. Honest. I guarantee that!</td></tr>

