<tr id="L377"><td><a href="#L377">377</a></td><td>KIRK:  Scotty, Bones. (and it's all the way around.) We're trapped. They got their way. We've got to stand and fight.</td></tr>

<tr id="L378"><td><a href="#L378">378</a></td><td>SCOTT:  Good. If they want a fight, let's gie'em a fight.</td></tr>

