<tr id="L406"><td><a href="#L406">406</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Your mind to my mind. Your thoughts to my thoughts.</td></tr>

<tr id="L407"><td><a href="#L407">407</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The marshalls gather as the lightning flashes and the wind blows.</td></tr>

<tr id="L408"><td><a href="#L408">408</a></td><td>SPOCK:  (to McCoy) The bullets are unreal. Without body. They are illusions only. Shadows without substance. They will not pass through your body, for they do not exist.</td></tr>

